Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.30,0:00:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Calling all pegasus ponies!\NMeeting tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.80,0:00:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Mandatory meeting\Nfor all Ponyville pegasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Library, tonight.\NBe cool, or be mule.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.32,0:00:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No offense.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.82,0:00:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,None taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.47,0:00:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, go on in, find a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.45,0:00:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You too, Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.39,0:00:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.46,0:00:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Season 2 | Episode 22\NHurricane Fluttershy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.29,0:01:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Subbed and Synced by GrayJeager\NGrayJeager@gmail.com
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.29,0:01:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,http://www.youtube.com/user/GrayJeager3\Nhttp://grayjeager.blogspot.fr
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.77,0:01:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Every living thing depends on\Nthe life-giving nourishment of rainwater.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.18,0:01:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And it is up to Cloudsdale\Nto provide rain-filled clouds{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.83,0:01:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to every corner of Equestria.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.19,0:01:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But how, one pony might ask,\Ndoes Cloudsdale gather all this extra water?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.52,0:01:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tornado power!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.71,0:01:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right, pegasi-driven tornado power.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.25,0:01:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A team of pegasi combine their wing power\Nto create a jumbo tornado,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.09,0:02:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}powerful enough to pull water\Nout of the local reservoir,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.39,0:02:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and funnel it all the way up to Cloudsdale.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.53,0:02:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Remember, pegasi,\Nyour jumbo tornado{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.57,0:02:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}must reach a minimum of\Neight hundred wing power{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.82,0:02:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to lift that water up to Cloudsdale.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.39,0:02:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So, the next time you're wondering{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.49,0:02:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Where does all that extra\Nrainwater come from?"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.82,0:02:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}just rememb-{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.53,0:02:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... intermission?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.26,0:02:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So, here's the scoop.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.81,0:02:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Cloudsdale has chosen\Nour own highland reservoir
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.70,0:02:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,as a source of the rainwater\Nthey need for all of Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.54,0:02:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And you know what that means.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.30,0:02:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It means it's up to Ponyville's pegasi\Nto bring that water up to Cloudsdale.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.84,0:02:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only that, but Spitfire,\Ncaptain of the Wonderbolts,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.23,0:02:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,will be here to oversee the water transfer\Nand record our top tornado windspeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.96,0:02:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Now last year, Fillydelphia\Nbroke the windspeed record
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.78,0:02:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,with a top speed of\Nnine hundred and ten wing power.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.49,0:02:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think we can do better.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.33,0:02:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we can get a top speed\Nover a thousand!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.36,0:03:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,IF each and every pony trains,\Nand trains hard
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.43,0:03:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,to get their wing power numbers up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.65,0:03:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That coughing better be from\Na popcorn kernel, Thunderlane.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.08,0:03:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Nopony's getting sick on my watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.06,0:03:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So, are we gonna train hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.61,0:03:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.81,0:03:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we gonna be strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.68,0:03:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.83,0:03:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we gonna be fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.48,0:03:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.34,0:03:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Record-smashing fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.17,0:03:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.57,0:03:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.18,0:03:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.78,0:03:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Stretch those glutes, Flitter!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.68,0:03:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice flexibility, Cloudchaser.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.97,0:03:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,A little too much flexibility,\NBlossomforth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.59,0:03:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Somepony give Blossomforth a hoof.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.97,0:03:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see some faster trotting,\NThunderlane!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.30,0:03:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Good pace, Silverspeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.87,0:03:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.93,0:04:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna need all the wing power\Nwe can get to break that record!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.08,0:04:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.98,0:04:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work, everypony!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.15,0:04:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Everypony except Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.32,0:04:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy? I know you're in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.00,0:04:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You're avoiding tornado duty\Nand I want to know why!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.76,0:04:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy, open-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.53,0:04:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Rainbow Dash.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.02,0:04:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy, what happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.88,0:04:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I...\NI think I have the pony pox.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.75,0:04:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I really, really wanted\Nto come to training day today...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.30,0:04:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But this pony pox has really\Nknocked me for a loop.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.83,0:04:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you poor thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.19,0:04:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, there's only\None cure for pony pox.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.20,0:04:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, plenty of bed-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.50,0:04:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Cold water!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.24,0:04:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Those pony pox are clearing right up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.32,0:05:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Y'know, all of a sudden I'm,\NI'm starting to feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.25,0:05:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just get out of these robes and-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.29,0:05:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,My wing, oh ow, it's hurt.\NI guess I can't fly after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.43,0:05:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Messed up wing, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.06,0:05:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop horsing around, Fluttershy.\NWe've got a lot of training to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.28,0:05:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on now, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.45,0:05:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, y'see, uh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.58,0:05:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash, I just can't do it!\NI can't fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.44,0:05:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.10,0:05:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Just last week you went into\Nthat wicked nose dive
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.61,0:05:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,to save that falling baby bird\Nright before it hit the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.10,0:05:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But that was different,\Nthat was an emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.74,0:05:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This whole tornado thing,\Nit's more like a performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.25,0:05:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And you know how I hate performing\Nin front of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.19,0:05:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you remember flight camp?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.14,0:05:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't gallop hard, or fly fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.54,0:05:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Not with everypony looking at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.09,0:05:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't that bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.80,0:05:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right, Rainbow Dash,\Nit wasn't bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.45,0:05:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was horrible!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.33,0:06:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All the other foals\Nused to tease me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.74,0:06:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}a lot!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.19,0:06:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fluttershy, Fluttershy,\NFluttershy can hardly fly!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.63,0:06:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can't risk that\Nsort of humiliation again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.63,0:06:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Suck it up, Fluttershy!\NThis is no time for-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.48,0:06:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, confidence or no confidence,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.58,0:06:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna need every pegasus\Nto break the record, including you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.08,0:06:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I need every ounce of wing power\NI can get.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.64,0:06:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so, Rainbow Dash...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.34,0:06:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.08,0:06:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.50,0:06:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.85,0:06:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- You will?\N- I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.64,0:06:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- You're game?\N- I'm game.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.28,0:06:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.72,0:07:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly does this machine do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.68,0:07:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an anemometer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.59,0:07:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It measures your accelerative velocity\Nand translates it into wing power.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.72,0:07:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus gauging your cumulative H2O\Nanti-gravitational potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.83,0:07:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Any other questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.56,0:07:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.72,0:07:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly does this machine do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.61,0:07:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It tells you how fast you're flying\Nand how strong your wings are.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.53,0:07:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that you again, Thunderlane?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.86,0:07:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, we need to have\Na germ-free environment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.51,0:07:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't me, it was Blossomforth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.74,0:07:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.48,0:07:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thunder Lane is just cooking up an excuse\Nto spend tornado day in bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.21,0:07:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you get over here\Nand be our first test flier, Thunderlane?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.40,0:07:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We have 9.3 wing power.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.81,0:07:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! That's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.21,0:08:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.16,0:08:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad...not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.67,0:08:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,16.5 wing power!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.51,0:08:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Now listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.86,0:08:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If each of you can get your numbers\Nup to at least 10.0 wing power
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.09,0:08:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,by the end of the week,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.25,0:08:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll no doubt set\Na new tornado speed record.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.72,0:08:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be number one!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.98,0:09:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive.\NFluttershy, your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.68,0:09:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy, Fluttershy,\NFluttershy can hardly fly...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.67,0:09:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- Tell her!\N- No, you tell her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.95,0:09:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.44,0:09:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Great job, Fluttershy!\NYou measured... point five.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.19,0:09:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Point five? Isn't that like...\Nless than one?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.52,0:10:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fluttershy, Fluttershy,\NFluttershy can hardly fly!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.91,0:10:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.65,0:10:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So some punks poked a little fun at you\Nand you got stage fright, big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.04,0:10:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You aren't gonna go quit\Njust because of that, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.86,0:10:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.45,0:10:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But I need you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.40,0:10:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Rainbow Dash, I just\Ndon't have the courage right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.11,0:10:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you, but I'm afraid\Na couple of little acorns won't solve
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.86,0:11:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,my big flying problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.77,0:11:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried, but you should've seen\Nthose ponies laughing at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.17,0:11:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's important\Nto have confidence in myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.21,0:11:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, I do remember.\NThe river was swelling...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.77,0:11:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,... and you were scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.37,0:11:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I did tell you to never give up
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.07,0:11:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and to believe in yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.40,0:11:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right, my friends.\NI shouldn't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.83,0:11:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I will get my confidence up and show\Neverypony that I am a good flyer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.51,0:11:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,A great flyer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.24,0:13:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's wonderful, Flitter.\NMuch better than yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.44,0:13:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This is crazy awesome!\NWe're gonna smash that record!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.82,0:13:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd he say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.99,0:13:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I look like I speak squirrel?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.48,0:13:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.92,0:13:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Two point three? Two point three?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.89,0:13:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That has to be some kind of mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.97,0:13:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I worked so hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.05,0:13:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy, that's a huge improvement!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.76,0:13:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You did awesome, Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.43,0:13:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No I didn't. I thought I'd\Ngotten over my nerves,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.66,0:13:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,but they still got the best of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.65,0:13:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I'll fly with\N10.0 wing power tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.42,0:13:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So you won't fly with 10.0 wing power.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.52,0:14:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Every bit counts!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.29,0:14:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How would you feel if everypony\Nelse was flying with 10.0 wing power
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.78,0:14:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and you were flying with 2.5?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.97,0:14:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, it was only 2.3, and- ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.51,0:14:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, uh... I'd feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.59,0:14:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly! Humiliated!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.05,0:14:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Rainbow Dash,\NI just can't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.22,0:14:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, Rainbow Dash.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.62,0:14:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You've still got plenty of\Nwing power for your tornado.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.67,0:14:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be able to lift tons of water up\Nto Cloudsdale!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.30,0:14:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If only there was a way to lift\NFluttershy out of the dumps...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.78,0:14:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we ready to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.92,0:14:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.19,0:15:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Lazy Thunderlane!\NWhere is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.98,0:15:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been trying to get out\Nof tornado duty the whole time
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.89,0:15:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,with his fake coughing and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.43,0:15:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Rumble, where's your lazy brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.28,0:15:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He's got the feather flu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.81,0:15:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He's down at Ponyville hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.76,0:15:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But he's not the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.00,0:15:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see, with those eight sick pegasi\Nout with the feather flu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.16,0:15:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.98,0:15:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me we won't be able\Nto break the windspeed record?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.83,0:15:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.57,0:15:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You might not have enough wing power\Nto create a tornado powerful enough
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.76,0:15:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,to lift the water to Cloudsdale!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.17,0:15:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, should we pack up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.56,0:15:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Of course not.\NForget the record.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.64,0:15:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Cloudsdale still needs water!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.42,0:15:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, everypony,\Nlet's give it all we've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.47,0:15:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,On the sound of the horn, we take off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.43,0:16:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You think they're gonna make it\Nto eight hundred wing power?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.97,0:16:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I sure hope so!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.38,0:16:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,One hundred and fifty wing power.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.46,0:16:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Two hundred and fifty wing power.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.76,0:16:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Five hundred wing power!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.94,0:16:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Seven hundred and fifty wing power!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.08,0:16:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.34,0:16:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy! What are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.53,0:16:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured, if I couldn't help\NRainbow Dash with the tornado,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.91,0:16:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the least I could do\Nwas offer moral support!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.46,0:16:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,She could sure use it,\Nconsidering eight pegasi
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.29,0:16:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,are sick with the feather flu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.31,0:16:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! That's terrible news!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.84,0:17:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.87,0:17:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You were so close to the\Neight hundred wing power minimum!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.89,0:17:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Rainbow Dash.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.80,0:17:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got to try again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.34,0:17:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But you've pushed your crew\Nto their limit already!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.88,0:17:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If you break apart again,\Nsomepony could get hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.77,0:17:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You should quit, it's not safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.12,0:17:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No! One more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.29,0:17:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gotta know we gave it our all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.22,0:17:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm going down, I'm going down flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.52,0:17:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, ponies, let's make this happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.70,0:17:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.62,0:17:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, here we go...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.75,0:17:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,One hundred wing power!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.31,0:17:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Two hundred... five hundred!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.45,0:17:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay in position!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.71,0:18:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Flap those wings! Faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.76,0:18:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Seven hundred!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.23,0:18:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Seven hundred and fifty wing power!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.25,0:18:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They fell apart right after this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.78,0:18:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm too nervous to look!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.27,0:18:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon! Just a little harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.55,0:18:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see the water\Ntrying to funnel through!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.72,0:18:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Seven ninety five! We are so close!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.91,0:18:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy, they need you up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.48,0:18:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't make a difference!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.12,0:18:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You can make a difference!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.34,0:18:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,My measly 2.3 wing power\Nis still too little!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.35,0:18:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sticking at seven ninety five!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.64,0:18:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if they've got\Nany more in 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.55,0:18:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it for Equestria!\NDo it for Rainbow Dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.00,0:18:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it for yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.77,0:19:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's moving!\NShe's doing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.69,0:19:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Seven ninety eight!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.27,0:19:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She surpassed her best\Nwing power number!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.77,0:19:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fluttershy, Fluttershy,\NFluttershy can hardly fly!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.85,0:19:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.54,0:19:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.85,0:19:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it was Fluttershy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.69,0:20:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,She did it! She did it!\NThey all did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.58,0:20:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, girl, take it easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.62,0:20:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Whuh, what? Did we do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.52,0:20:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we did it!\NYou did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.33,0:20:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Great job, Fluttershy,\Nthat was awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.28,0:20:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we couldn't have done it\Nwithout you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.73,0:20:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice job, Rainbow Dash.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.08,0:20:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You may not have set a new record,\Nbut you showed a lot of guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.70,0:20:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.80,0:20:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you wanna talk guts,\Nthen you've gotta give it
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.69,0:20:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,to my number one flyer,\NFluttershy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.18,0:21:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hear it for Fluttershy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.92,0:21:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy! Fluttershy!\NFluttershy can really fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.53,0:21:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dear Princess Celestia,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.32,0:21:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}sometimes you can feel like\Nwhat you have to offer{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.85,0:21:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}is too little to make a difference.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.32,0:21:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But today, I learned that\Neverypony's contribution is important.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.36,0:21:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No matter how small.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.95,0:21:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you just keep your head high,\Ndo your best, and believe in yourself,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.42,0:21:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}anything can happen.{\i0}
